caller_intent: Dina from Alliance Insurance needs to make a payment on a canceled Auto Owners Insurance account (103610335) that is awaiting reinstatement after receiving a signed statement of no loss. She seeks confirmation if the payment can be processed immediately or if she must wait for underwriting approval.
resolution_steps: Agent Lisa confirms the account is marked as canceled in the system despite verbal approval for reinstatement.
Lisa attempts to locate Kelly Jenny (underwriter) in the underwriting division to notify her about the pending payment.
After finding Kelly Jenny's extension (50622), Lisa transfers Dina to the underwriter.
Dina leaves a voicemail for Kelly Jenny with account details and payment information.
knowledge_required: Understanding Auto Owners Insurance account statuses (canceled vs. reinstated)
Internal system navigation for underwriter lookups
Payment processing limitations for canceled accounts
systems_referenced: Auto Owners Insurance policy/account management system
Phone system with extension lookup capabilities
summary: Dina from Alliance Insurance attempts to process a payment on a canceled Auto Owners account awaiting reinstatement. The agent confirms the account requires an underwriting flag to be active before processing. After locating the responsible underwriter, Dina is transferred to leave a voicemail for final approval. The payment remains pending until the underwriting flag is activated.
